Name: Asian Food Cart Tycoon
About the game: Sate (Satay) is the most popular food in Indonesia and some countries in Asia. In this game you will build a business from scratch to become successful! Improve your business facilities, advertise your business, meet various kinds of customers day or night and do the available daily missions. Features: Manage and develop your satay business Upgrade your facilities Lots of characters Advertise your business Daily missions Meet the VIP! Collect some airdrops Day and night cycle And most importantly, collect the money and make your satay business the best in the world!
